{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Santiago Ferreira","author":"Santiago Ferreira"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"b10b6f76-9b3f-55fa-823a-1e0e9824e1d0","excerpt":"A fast website with a minimal designI built this website from the ground up to explore and learn new client-side technologies. I’m very glad I decided to use…","html":"<h3>A fast website with a minimal design</h3>\n<p>I built this website from the ground up to explore and learn new client-side technologies. I’m very glad I decided to use <strong>Gatsby</strong> which continues to be one of my favorite ways of building web sites and web apps. All the content on the site is organized as <strong>Markdown</strong> files, images and folders.</p>\n<p>Another tool that I used for the first time on this site is <strong>Theme UI</strong>, along with <strong>Styled Components</strong>.</p>\n<p>Check out the site here:</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://santiandtugce.com/\">https://santiandtugce.com/</a></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Gatsby Website","date":"May 08, 2019","description":"Artist website built with Gatsby","technologies":["Gatsby","TypeScript","Theme UI","Markdown"],"thumbnail":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/png;base64,","aspectRatio":2,"src":"/static/491abc5c8d7ea6d8b62d1dfdb5f549e9/40a76/static-website-cover-horizontal-01.png","srcSet":"/static/491abc5c8d7ea6d8b62d1dfdb5f549e9/c972b/static-website-cover-horizontal-01.png 340w,\n/static/491abc5c8d7ea6d8b62d1dfdb5f549e9/27625/static-website-cover-horizontal-01.png 680w,\n/static/491abc5c8d7ea6d8b62d1dfdb5f549e9/40a76/static-website-cover-horizontal-01.png 1360w,\n/static/491abc5c8d7ea6d8b62d1dfdb5f549e9/1e49b/static-website-cover-horizontal-01.png 2040w,\n/static/491abc5c8d7ea6d8b62d1dfdb5f549e9/7148e/static-website-cover-horizontal-01.png 2720w,\n/static/491abc5c8d7ea6d8b62d1dfdb5f549e9/fb0be/static-website-cover-horizontal-01.png 4000w","sizes":"(max-width: 1360px) 100vw, 1360px"}}}}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"s